 3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who likes red##2
 5. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the lawyer##1
 8. the writer is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the right of the dancer##1
11. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
12. the social-worker is on the left of the dancer##1
13. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
