.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: aconite, begonia, sunflower, rose, daffodil
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, entrepreneur, fisherman, pilot
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, crime, fantasy, scientific
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: ambient, blues, hip-hop, house, trance
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 2. the fisherman is between the person watching crime movies and the entrepreneur##2
 3. the person who growsrose is the fisherman##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the fan of house##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is in the middle##1
 6. the person who growsrose is between the pilot and the fan of blues##2
 7. the fan of house is the person who growssunflower##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is the fan of hip-hop##1
 9. the fan of ambient is on the left of the pilot##1
10. the bartender is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
11. the entrepreneur is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1
13. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Flower      | aconite      | begonia         | rose      | sunflower | daffodil     |
| Job           | engineer | entrepreneur | fisherman | pilot    | bartender  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy  | animation    | adventure | crime    | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop  | blues        | ambient   | house    | trance     |

